$X=\left(\frac{\alpha}{\alpha+\beta}\right)\frac{M}{P_X}=\left(\frac{1}{1+2}\right)\frac{90}{1}=30$ & $X=\left(\frac{\alpha}{\alpha+\beta}\right)\frac{M}{P_X}=\left(\frac{\frac{1}{2}}{\frac{1}{2}+\frac{1}{2}}\right)\frac{100}{1}=50$ \\ 
